													<p>
					The European Games Award is the first award exclusively for European video and computer game developers, which lets professionals and gamers from all over Europe participate in the voting for 										<a href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6&amp;Itemid=3">... Read >></a>
									</p>
			</div>
					
						
			<div class="gk_is_text_item">
															<h4><span><a href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4&amp;Itemid=6">Gamesload European Newcomer Award</a></span></h4>
													<p>
					With the Gamesload European Newcomer Award your team has the chance to win 2.500 € as prize money as well as a European-wide distribution deal with Gamesload if you achieve 										<a href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4&amp;Itemid=6">... Read >></a>
									</p>
			</div>
					
						
			<div class="gk_is_text_item">
															<h4><span><a href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9&amp;Itemid=8">Public Voting</a></span></h4>
													<p>
					The European Games Award will make a European-wide public voting possible for the first time. Registered EGA website users will not only vote online for the best action, sports, adventure 										<a href="/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9&amp;Itemid=8">... Read >></a>
									</p>
